description: Nestled in the heart of one of Boston’s most sought after and convenient neighborhoods, this spacious 2 bed, 2 bath “Southie” condo has it all. The nearly 1400 square feet of living space at 509 E 2nd feels like *much* more with its 10ft ceilings and oversized windows which perfectly filters in the morning light. Recently renovated from top to bottom, this young, 2012 condo exudes contemporary elegance with a handsomely updated chefs kitchen complete with Viking appliances, a new spa-like master and guest bathrooms, newly finished floors and freshly painted interior. Outside, new owners of 509 E 2nd will enjoy a meticulously maintained private, fenced in patio, perfect for entertaining, grilling and letting the dogs and/or children play safely. Access your city home with ease by effortlessly pulling into the oversized, heated garage and swing into your private, deeded parking space, complete with electric car charging capabilities, and take the elevator directly up to your unit
